# Escrowly Backend - Cursor Project Rules

# These rules ensure consistency across all services in the monorepo

## Project Architecture

### Monorepo Structure

```
escrowly-backend/
├── packages/                    # Shared packages (npm workspaces)
│   └── shared-config/           # Shared config, secrets, utilities
├── services/                    # Microservices
│   ├── auth/                    # Authentication service (port 3000)
│   ├── admin/                   # Admin service - blogs, help-desk (port 3002)
│   ├── bff/                     # Backend-for-Frontend - API gateway (port 3001)
│   ├── escrow/                  # Escrow service (future)
│   ├── wallet/                  # Wallet service (future)
│   └── ledger/  
│   └── inquiry/                  # inquiry  service (future)
│   └── notification/              # notification  service (future)

├── infra/                       # AWS CDK infrastructure
├── scripts/                     # Utility scripts (backups, migrations)
└── docker-compose.yml           # Local/EC2 orchestration
```

### Service Structure (follow auth/admin pattern)

```
services/<service-name>/
├── src/
│   ├── main.ts                  # Entry point
│   ├── app.module.ts            # Root module
│   ├── app.controller.ts        # Root controller
│   ├── app.service.ts           # Root service
│   ├── common/                  # Shared utilities, guards, decorators
│   │   ├── decorators/
│   │   ├── guards/
│   │   ├── interceptors/
│   │   └── index.ts
│   ├── health/                  # Health check module
│   │   ├── health.controller.ts
│   │   ├── health.service.ts
│   │   ├── health.module.ts
│   │   └── index.ts
│   ├── prisma/                  # Prisma module (if service uses DB)
│   │   ├── prisma.service.ts
│   │   ├── prisma.module.ts
│   │   └── index.ts
│   └── <feature>/               # Feature modules
│       ├── dto/
│       │   ├── create-<entity>.dto.ts
│       │   ├── update-<entity>.dto.ts
│       │   ├── <entity>-response.dto.ts
│       │   └── index.ts
│       ├── <feature>.controller.ts
│       ├── <feature>.service.ts
│       ├── <feature>.module.ts
│       └── index.ts
├── prisma/
